For questions 4–6, factor the expression.

  1. \(15x^3y − 3x^2y^2 + 6xy^3\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit 6.4.3.

The correct answer is \(3xy(5x^2 − xy + 2y^2)\).

  1. \(−7a^3 + 21a^2 − 14a\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit 6.4.3.

The correct answer is \(−7a(a^2 − 3a + 2)\).

  1. \(8n(n − 4) + 5(n − 4)\)

Correct!

Try again. Revisit 6.4.3.

The correct answer is \((n − 4)(8n + 5)\).
